<div id="pf38a6" class="pf w55 h238" data-page-no="38a6"><div class="pc pc38a6 w55 h238"><div class="t mcd1 xd4 h104 y2b0b ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">PRAYER- </div><div class="t m191a xd4 h104 y2b8b ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A TWO-WAY </div><div class="t m165e xd4 h104 y2457 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">CHANNEL </div><div class="t m1f0 xba h46 y2b0c ff2 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 7 </div><div class="t m351 xdc h1c y2b6c ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">February 11-17 </div><div class="t ma52 x0 h20 y1a5 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I will hear what God the Lord will </div><div class="t m32e xd4 h20 y5d7 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">speak: for he will speak peace unto his </div><div class="t m88b xd4 h20 ye5c ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people, and to his saints: but let them </div><div class="t m86b xd4 h20 y2a8 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not turn again to folly.&quot; Ps. 85:8. </div><div class="t m1c6 x0 h1c y21c ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Some regard prayer as a way of chang-</div><div class="t mfd5 xd4 h1c y3f5 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing God&apos;s mind, or of conveying to Him </div><div class="t m1479 xd4 h1c y70 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our condition as if He were ignorant of </div><div class="t m9b6 xd4 h1c y2ec ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it. This is a deception. &quot;Prayer is the open-</div><div class="t m39b xd4 h1c y2c6 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing of the heart to God as to a friend. Not </div><div class="t m9a4 xd4 h1c y37f ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that it is necessary in order to make known </div><div class="t m465 xd4 h1c y713 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to God what we are, but in order to enable </div><div class="t m2d4 xd4 h1c ye5d ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us to receive Him. Prayer does not bring </div><div class="t m1856 xd4 h1c y2f ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God down to us, but brings us up to </div><div class="t mdb1 xd3 h1c y276 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him.&quot;—Steps to Christ, </div><div class="t m99f x5e h1c y276 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 93. God </div><div class="t m52e xd3 h1c yc66 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stands ever ready to help His children. </div><div class="t m6a8 xd3 h1c ya0 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through prayer we unlock the storehouse </div><div class="t me20 xd3 h1c y716 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of heaven&apos;s riches by acquainting our-</div><div class="t m450 xd3 h1c y189 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">selves with them, by bringing our lives into </div><div class="t m20b xd3 h1c y225 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conformity with God&apos;s will, by understand-</div><div class="t m27b xd3 h1c y2ce ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing and applying the promises of God. </div><div class="t m3c5 xb9 h1c y40 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prayer is communication and commun-</div><div class="t m320 xd3 h1c y42 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ion with God. We speak, we listen, we hear. </div><div class="t m595 xd3 h1c y45b ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prayer grows more and more important  </div><div class="t ma59 x2b h1c y67 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to us as we discover its true purpose. </div><div class="t ma80 x2b h1c y6a ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When we cease to regard prayer simply </div><div class="t mbc8 x2b h1c y235 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as our telling God something, and look </div><div class="t m3a7 x2b h1c ye8 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for Him to return the conversation through </div><div class="t m1159 x2b h1c y5c5 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit and the Word, then we shall </div><div class="t m1317 x2b h1c y251 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">indeed &quot;pray without ceasing.&quot; </div><div class="t md2e x2b h20 y21e ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHTS </div><div class="t m1c8 x20 h1c y2102 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Will. </div><div class="t mce0 x95 h1c y84e ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Bring your lives into har-</div><div class="t mb77 x2b h1c y37f ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mony with your petitions, that you may </div><div class="t mbcc x2b h1c y713 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">receive the blessings for which you </div><div class="t m602 x1f h1c ye5d ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pray.&quot;—Testimonies, </div><div class="t m787 xa1 h1c y1e2 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Vol. 7, p. 274. Dis-</div><div class="t m995 x1f h1c y2d ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">covering the will of God is one great pur-</div><div class="t md1 x2b h1c y715 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pose of prayer. </div><div class="t m599 x20 h1c yc66 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Access to </div><div class="t m80c xa3 h1c y296 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. &quot;Every prayer in behalf </div><div class="t m289 x1f h1c y204 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the suffering and oppressed is reported </div><div class="t m570 x1f h1c y169 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before the eternal throne and placed on </div><div class="t m1176 x2b h1c yc49 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heaven&apos;s imperishable record.&quot;—Testi-</div><div class="t m596 x2b h1c y5be ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">monies, </div><div class="t m571 x9f h1c y5be ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Vol. 5, p. 133. God does </div><div class="t m478 xe8 h1c y5be ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hear </div><div class="t m385 x1a3 h1c y5be ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t m3b4 x2b h1c y2ce ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">answer. </div><div class="t mb9 x20 h1c y35d ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Communion With God. </div><div class="t m1176 x25 h1c y14ae ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Prayer is the </div><div class="t m1ca x1f h1c ye1e ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opening of the heart . . . as to a friend.&quot;—</div><div class="t m58f x2b h1c y45c ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Steps to Christ, </div><div class="t m856 x57 h1c ye22 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 93. </div><div class="t mdcf x15e h1c ye2a ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">53 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
